  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/50px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/75px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/100px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Barba Bolton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/50px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/75px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/100px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Barba Bolton by Debustee.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3d/Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png/350px-Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"502\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3d/Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png/525px-Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3d/Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png/700px-Barba_Bolton_by_Debustee.png 2x\" /></a><div>Barba Bolton, by Debustee ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Barba Bolton</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Barba_Bolton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_Ball\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day Ball\">Maiden's Day Ball</a> was held at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> to find a second wife and new queen for King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>. Many <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maidens</a> across <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> came to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> in hopes of marrying the young king. However, the event was not a true ball, but merely a procession of maidens, each woman curtsying before the king while a <a href=\"/index.php/Herald\" title=\"Herald\">herald</a> announced her name and lineage. Barba was one of these maidens, but she took the opportunity to ask Aegon that if he did not choose her, to at least send <a href=\"/index.php/Food\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Food\">food</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>, as the region was suffering greatly from <a href=\"/index.php/Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Winter\">winter</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quote\">Quote</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Barba_Bolton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quote\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>If you send me <a href=\"/index.php/Dreadfort\" title=\"Dreadfort\">home</a>, Your Grace, send me home with food, for the snows are deep and <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">your people</a> are starving.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Barba to <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Barba_Bolton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Barba_Bolton\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Barba Bolton</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404161052\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.078 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.269 seconds\nPreprocessor visi